EnNuHX9NDMhlDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=feffed45\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sport1.de/fussball/champions-league/2017/03/fc-bayern-real-madrid-fuer-karl-heinz-rummenigge-die-nummer-eins</a>"},{"pid":"b006016b5cc9c84dc418215982fcaa0189c2e1b5","tid":618003,"uid":153400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T22:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}